quran[23{c,v,t}:
26,137,yeh baatein to yun hi hoti chali aayi hain
26,138,"aur hum azaab mein mubtala honay walay nahi hain """
26,139,"aakhir kaar unhon ne ussay jhutla diya aur hum ne un ko halaak kar diya yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar log maan-ne walay nahi hain"
26,140,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
26,141,smod ne Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya
26,142,"yaad karo jabkay un ke bhai saleh ne un se kaha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
26,143,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
26,144,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
26,145,"mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi, mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai"
26,146,"kya tum unn sab cheezon ke darmain, jo yahan hain, bas yun hi itminan se rehne diye jao ge ?"
26,147,inn baghoon aur chashmon mein ?
26,148,inn khaiton aur nkhlstanon mein jin ke khoshay ras bharay hain ?
26,149,tum pahar khoud khoud kar fakharya unn mein emiratein banatay ho
26,150,Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
26,151,unn be lagaam logon ki itaat nah karo
26,152,"jo zameen mein fasaad barpaa karte hain aur koi islaah nahi karte """
26,153,"unhon ne jawab diya"" to mehez aik sehar zada aadmi hai"
26,154,"to hum jaisay aik ensaan ke siwa aur kya hai laa koi nishani agar to schcha hai """
26,155,"saleh ne kaha"" yeh oontni hai aik din is ke peenay ka hai aur aik din tum sab ke pani lainay ka"
26,156,"is ko hargiz nah chhairna warna aik barray din ka azaab tum ko aa le ga """
26,157,magar unhon ne is ki kochin kaat den aur aakhir kaar pachhtatey reh gay
26,158,"azaab ne inhen aa liya yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar maan-ne walay nahi"
26,159,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
